  "title": "Part Time Office Admin",
  "description": "<p>Job Descriptions:</p><p><strong>Administrative Support</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle day-to-day administrative and clerical duties</p></li><li><p>Manage incoming calls, emails, mail, and office correspondence</p></li><li><p>Prepare, file, and maintain documents, records, and reports</p></li><li><p>Support management with scheduling, meeting coordination, and minutes taking</p></li></ul><p><strong>Office Operations</strong></p><ul><li><p>Maintain office supplies, pantry items, and vendor relationships</p></li><li><p>Coordinate office maintenance, repairs, and service providers</p></li><li><p>Ensure office facilities are clean, functional, and well-organised</p></li><li><p>Manage access cards, keys, and office equipment</p></li></ul><p><strong>Coordination & Support</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist in onboarding of new staff (workspace setup, admin documentation)</p></li><li><p>Coordinate internal events, meetings, and company activities</p></li><li><p>Liaise with external partners, suppliers, and service providers</p></li><li><p>Support HR or Finance teams with basic admin tasks when required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Social Media:</strong></p><p>Implement social media strategies aligned with the company’s overall marketing goals.</p><p>Create engaging and visually appealing content, including  graphics, videos, articles, and posts, tailored to each social media  platform.</p><p>Manage social media activities, including posting content, monitoring engagement, and responding to comments and messages.</p><p><strong>Compliance & Documentation:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Ensure proper filing and record-keeping in line with company policies</p></li><li><p>Assist with audit preparation and compliance documentation</p></li><li><p>Maintain confidentiality of sensitive information</p></li></ul><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>Basic computer skills</li><li>Social Media Savvy</li><li>Fluent in English</li><li>Basic Design skills using Canvas</li><li>Basic Video Editing Skills using Capcut</li><li>Singaporeans / PRs</li></ul>",
